title: Delete Duplicates for Microsoft Outlook v3.4.0.1
description:
Delete Duplicates for Microsoft Outlook v3.4.0.1

Features

? Fast search & powerful performances
? Friendly & intuitive interface - Features mailboxes-tree panel & mailbox-information panel
? Two major scanning methods - Compare the message text (Standard) or just the message-id&#039;s (Light)
? Optionally compare full RFC headers
? Provision to exclude custom headers from comparison
? Optionally compare message attachments by content
? Provision to exclude custom attachments from comparison
? Cross-mailbox scan - Compare for duplicates across several mailboxes
? Prioritize mailboxes - Decide where to keep the originals
? Variety of filters - Will let you narrow the search and nail down duplicates
? Variety of actions - Determine what to do with duplicates
? Support for Outlook versions: 2000/2/3/7
? Use of Regular Expression
? Extra Tweaks - Additional scanning options & optimizations
? Wizard-free interface
? Logging
and more...
